data.meta_description: Since 1934, Annalee Dolls has been bringing smiles to young and old. Discover great seasonal gifts and home decorations. Shop now!

Homepage

SUMMER WAREHOUSE SALE

UP TO 70% OFF

The holiday season is sneaking up, and we need to make room in our warehouse. Enjoy enormous discounts during our Summer Warehouse Saleâ€” save up to 70% on designs for every season and holiday!

The Biggest Sale of the Year

SUMMER WAREHOUSE SALE

Item #360019

This 3 inch set of amber Indian mice are adorable in their birch tree canoe. She is wearing a doe skin dress with fringe on top as well as a brown head band with an orange feather in her hair. He is wearing buckskin pants with a brown head band with a purplish feather in his hair too! He is also holding a paddle. The canoe is on a blue felt base for added stability.

Fun item to use in any table top display; a mirrored base would make it appear as though they are actually canoing in water. They look really cute when paired with our Indian Girl and Indian Boy Mice too!

Facial expressions may vary

Our 9 inch chef Santa is whipping up a batch of gingerbread! He is wearing black pants, shoes and a white shirt covered with a Christmas plaid apron. His white chef's hat has a matching hatband and a holly berry accent. Two white and red flap designed pockets are on his apron; each has a gingerbread shape inside. He is holding a whisk that has some gingerbread batter left on it and a bowl with the word "Gingerbread" printed on it. Yum! What a traditional theme for our Sugar and Spice Chef Santa!

Wonderful item to use in a Christmas display especially on a kitchen shelf or on the hutch. Fun to display by itself; he looks even better when paired with our Sugar and Spice Mrs. Chef Santa! They would look great in a wreath too!

Facial expressions may vary.
